  "description": "This Node.js application serves as a backend for a Crypto Currency Converter, utilizing the CoinMarketCap free API. It provides a robust foundation for handling currency conversion logic, enabling users to convert amounts between various cryptocurrencies and fiat currencies such as USD, EUR, and more.",
